            "title": "財經｜據報沙特擬5月對中國原油銷售量減半",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜據報沙特擬5月對中國原油銷售量減半\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜據報沙特擬5月對中國原油銷售量減半</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博引述知情交易員報道，隨着中東戰事擾亂原油貿易流向並推高油價，全球最大原油出口國沙特阿拉伯計劃5月對最大進口國中國的原油銷售量減半，降至約2000萬桶原油。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">交易員稱，上述數量低於4月設定的約4000萬桶銷售量。亞洲煉油商被提供通過紅海港口裝運的僅有阿拉伯輕質原油這一油種。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據報，此次銷售下調發生在沙特阿美(Saudi Aramco)上調其原油官方售價之後。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%B2%99%E7%89%B9%E6%93%AC5%E6%9C%88%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8E%9F%E6%B2%B9%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E9%87%8F%E6%B8%9B%E5%8D%8A-071835509.html",
